4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring cybersecurity professionals with no prior experience. Over 16 weeks, students attend 3 live online classes per week, receiving practical training in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, as well as cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Participants learn to manage risks through data loss prevention strategies and navigate compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. The program awards an official completion certificate upon finishing and accommodates both English and Spanish speakers. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop